Vår projektledare professor Matti Tedre deltog i evenemanget "Digital Futures for Education" den 6.3.2024. Läs den ursprungliga nyhetstexten här: <a href="https://www.digitalfutures.kth.se/2024/05/27/digital-futures-for-education-explores-ais-impact-on-university-teaching-and-learning/">https://www.digitalfutures.kth.se/2024/05/27/digital-futures-for-education-explores-ais-impact-on-university-teaching-and-learning/</a>
